1. On je počeo da se zabavlja sa *djevojkom* (He started to have fun with the girl). 
2. Ona je sretno otišla sa svojom *djevojkom* (She happily left with her girlfriend).
3. Nisam mogao da prestane da razmišljam o *djevojci* (I couldn't stop thinking about the girl). 
4. Ona je vodila *djevojku* za ruku (She was holding the girl's hand). 
5. Imao je dvije *djevojke* za zabavu (He had two girls for fun).
6. On je ispričao svoju *djevojku* (He told his girlfriend).